漢羅台文: 越南捌有大約一千冬予中國封建王朝直接統治的北屬時期。
台羅: Ua̍t-lâm bat ū tāi-iok tsi̍t tshing tang hōo Tiong-kok hong-kiàn ông-tiâu ti̍t-tsiap thóng-tī ê Pak-sio̍k sî-kî.
台羅數字調: uat8-lam5 bat4 u7 tai7-iok4 tsit8 tshing1 tang1 hoo7 tiong1-kok4 hong1-kian3 ong5-tiau5 tit8-tsiap4 thong2-ti7 e5 pak4-siok8 si5-ki5.
白話字: Oa̍t-lâm bat ū tāi-iok chi̍t chheng tang hō͘ Tiong-kok hong-kiàn ông-tiâu ti̍t-chiap thóng-tī ê Pak-sio̍k sî-kî.
